    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_26_19384-19429",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "19384-19429",
      "markText": "“再审申请成功时，你知道检察官是怎么说的吗？他说，老是让死刑犯活着，才会发生这样的事……”",
      "totalCount": 2758,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=19384&rangeEnd=19429",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=19384&rangeEnd=19429"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_20_2012-2111",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2012-2111",
      "markText": "当年的案件使我知道，警方为自我保护会指鹿为马，媒体也会被警方提供的真假难辨的消息牢牢操控。日本司法系统与媒体联手修建起来的围墙坚不可摧，一介小小记者实在势单力薄。因此我执笔写书，只为将信息传递出去。",
      "totalCount": 2244,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2012&rangeEnd=2111",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2012&rangeEnd=2111"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_20_2317-2419",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2317-2419",
      "markText": "我最想说的是，在日本，声音最为微弱的五个无辜女孩从世上消失了。 我不会就此作罢。 绝对不会。",
      "totalCount": 1804,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2317&rangeEnd=2419",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2317&rangeEnd=2419"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_33_1252-1316",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "1252-1316",
      "markText": "依附于权力与官衔的怒吼，纵然不予理睬也会响彻四方。可那些微弱的声音却无法轻易传到社会的耳中。在两者之间架起桥梁，就是报道的使命。",
      "totalCount": 1781,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1252&rangeEnd=1316",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1252&rangeEnd=1316"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_27_19848-19882",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "19848-19882",
      "markText": "我再次感到恐惧。公权力一旦与媒体联手，不负责任的言论将在社会上蔓延。",
      "totalCount": 1704,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=19848&rangeEnd=19882",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=19848&rangeEnd=19882"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_31_3141-3203",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "3141-3203",
      "markText": "小川副大臣答道：“如果时效已过，就不能追诉。我不是说重新搜捕毫无意义，可找到嫌疑人，将其公之于众，难道不会产生人权问题吗？”",
      "totalCount": 1674,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=3141&rangeEnd=3203",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=3141&rangeEnd=3203"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_33_9223-9290",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "9223-9290",
      "markText": "我现在还不能揭露你是谁、你在哪儿。可是，我要在此记录下你的存在。 你逃不掉的！",
      "totalCount": 1600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=9223&rangeEnd=9290",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=9223&rangeEnd=9290"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_23_12319-12367",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "12319-12367",
      "markText": "作为记者，我不为他人的利益去采访报道，只以事实为依据。自打从事这份职业以来，我便牢记：兼听则明。",
      "totalCount": 1595,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=12319&rangeEnd=12367",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=12319&rangeEnd=12367"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_32_22043-22112",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "22043-22112",
      "markText": "严刑逼供的警察、对供述内容深信不疑的检方与法院、跟风报道的媒体……我切身体会到现实的严酷——纵然被判无罪，也无法让每个人都相信他是清白的。",
      "totalCount": 1425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=22043&rangeEnd=22112",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=22043&rangeEnd=22112"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_28_1870-1912",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "1870-1912",
      "markText": "母亲横山光子为由佳梨准备了各个年龄段的衣服，这样，不论她什么时候回来，都有衣服可穿。",
      "totalCount": 1410,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1870&rangeEnd=1912",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1870&rangeEnd=1912"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_28_19897-19970",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "19897-19970",
      "markText": "“我忍受了十七年，希望警方能向我道歉。被捕后不久，我父亲就去世了，两年前，我母亲也走了……一句搞错了就可以没事了吗？我想要他们把我的人生还给我。”",
      "totalCount": 1397,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=19897&rangeEnd=19970",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=19897&rangeEnd=19970"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_26_14909-15000",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "14909-15000",
      "markText": "我还剩两千日元的税没交，麻烦你们帮我交一下。我给市政府添麻烦了，税金就拜托你们了。 菅家身陷囹圄，居然还在担心自己滞纳的税金。",
      "totalCount": 1368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300035133&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=14909&rangeEnd=15000",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e0d32970813ab7439g013534?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=14909&rangeEnd=15000"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300035133_31_9092-9185",
      "chapterUid": 31,
